  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to collect information on the safety, tolerability and
      immunogenicity of an investigational smallpox vaccine at different doses and using different
      routes of administration in vaccinia-naive and vaccinated healthy volunteers
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
